  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: You seem earnest, which is either admirable or catastrophic.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: 'So I will spare you one mistake: do not ignore the corridor behind the
      counter.'
  choices:
  - choiceText: All right. I will remember that.
